      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I'm being serious though... sometimes it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and the feeling in my chest is to just... quit. Not just taking a nap or a break, but like, giving up on everything for good. Is it ever actually okay to do that? To just stop trying?",
